text: Morazán is a 2017 Honduran historical drama movie directed by Hispano Durón and starring Orlando Valenzuela (in the title role), Tito Estrada, Melissa Merlo, Gabriel Ochoa. ==Other websites== * Category:2017 drama movies Category:2010s historical movies Category:Honduran movies Category:Movies set in the 1840s
